a name="about"
.intro-header
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12
        .intro-message
          h1 Woobox Votes CSV Converter
          h3 Use the file upload field below to upload your Woobox CSV.
          h3 Locations will be added as a new column to the CSV and the file will download automatically.
          hr.intro-divider/

    .row
      .col-lg-3
      .col-lg-6
        = form_for :locator, url: locators_path, method: :post, html: { multipart: true, class: 'form-inline' } do
          .form-group
            = file_field_tag 'votes_csv', class: 'btn btn-default'

          = submit_tag 'Convert', class: 'btn btn-primary'
      .col-lg-3


  /! /.container
/! /.intro-header
/! Page Content
a name="services"
.content-section-a
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-5.col-sm-6
        hr.section-heading-spacer/
        .clearfix
        h2.section-heading
          | How to export the Woobox votes file...
        p.lead
          | Log in to your Woobox account and click&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-success  Manage
          |  on the campaign you wish to export.
      .col-lg-5.col-lg-offset-2.col-sm-6
        = image_tag 'woobox-step-1.jpg', class: 'img-responsive'
  /! /.container
/! /.content-section-a
.content-section-b
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-5.col-lg-offset-1.col-sm-push-6.col-sm-6
        hr.section-heading-spacer/
        .clearfix
        h2.section-heading
          | Navigate to Download Exports page...
        p.lead
          | In the campaign management screen on the left side bar, click on&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-default  Export
          |  and then click on&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-default  Download Exports
      .col-lg-5.col-sm-pull-6.col-sm-6
        = image_tag 'woobox-step-2.jpg', class: 'img-responsive'
  /! /.container
/! /.content-section-b
.content-section-a
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-5.col-sm-6
        hr.section-heading-spacer/
        .clearfix
        h2.section-heading
          | Generate the export file...
        p.lead
          | In the Download Exports page click on the&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-default  Download
          |  button of the&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-default  Export Votes
          |  box. It should then turn into a&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-default  Refresh Status
          |  button. Wait a few seconds and click it to check the export status.
      .col-lg-5.col-lg-offset-2.col-sm-6
        = image_tag 'woobox-step-3.jpg', class: 'img-responsive'
  /! /.container
/! /.content-section-a
.content-section-b
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-5.col-lg-offset-1.col-sm-push-6.col-sm-6
        hr.section-heading-spacer/
        .clearfix
        h2.section-heading
          | Download the export file...
        p.lead
          | After waiting a minute, the&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-default  Refresh Status
          |  button will turn into a&nbsp;
          span.badge.alert-default  Download
          |  button. Click it and your Votes CSV file will download.
      .col-lg-5.col-sm-pull-6.col-sm-6
        = image_tag 'woobox-step-4.jpg', class: 'img-responsive'
  /! /.container
/! /.content-section-b

a name="contact"
.banner
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12
        h2 Now you have the downloaded zip file. You have to unzip it first and then upload at the top of this page!

